      "id": 66038,
      "name": "lonewolfcyclist",
      "username": "lonewolfcyclist",
      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/lonewolfcyclist/{size}/10677_2.png",
      "created_at": "2024-12-21T12:04:56.075Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m not sure why my HRM sometimes gets disconnected after a pause (e.g., to eat or refill water, which takes a few minutes). When I get back and start pedaling again, my heart rate doesn\u2019t show anymore. I tried restarting my armband HRM and reconnecting it, but the TrainerDay (TD) app couldn\u2019t find it. So, I added another HRM, and it worked. That was the first instance, which happened the other day.</p>\n<p>Earlier today, I did a workout using the second HRM. I took a break in the middle of the workout, and the same issue happened again. I then re-added the original HRM that had disconnected during my previous ride.</p>\n<p>When I looked at the number of sensors, it showed four (circled in the screenshot below). This suggests that, for some reason, the HRM is connected but not displaying in the list.</p>\n<p>I\u2019m using an iPhone 13 with two heart rate monitors: my Forerunner 165 and an armband HRM by Coopsco.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9.png\" data-download-href=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9\" title=\"IMG_8617\"><img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9_2_231x500.png\" alt=\"IMG_8617\" data-base62-sha1=\"38IH4c7WECaNsnsPFU5yiHJL91v\" width=\"231\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9_2_231x500.png, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9_2_346x750.png 1.5x, https://forums.trainerday.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1602e3a8f58e11e3c0b02c1977026317ed4258f9_2_462x1000.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"242730\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far