      "created_at": "2024-12-21T12:46:06.444Z",
      "cooked": "<p>We have a new version of our app coming out and we changed the way connections work significantly.  This seems to be a rare issue but you are not the only one.  We don\u2019t know why this only affects a small number of people but hopefully this new version resolves it. Probably out after the new years.  We are testing it now.</p>\n<p>Another solution people find might resolve this is uninstalling our app and re-installing.  No idea why but this can occasionally help as well.</p>",
